---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About" description="Learn about Gemini Home Improvements and my commitment to quality">
	<section class="hero" style="padding: 3rem 0;">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About</h1>
			<p>Quality workmanship since 2008</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="grid grid-2">
				<div>
					<h2>My Story</h2>
					<p>
						Gemini Home Improvements was founded in 2008 with a simple mission: 
						to provide homeowners in the Greater Toronto Area with high-quality 
						exterior renovation services at fair prices.
					</p>
					<p>
						Over the past 15+ years, I've built a reputation on quality workmanship 
						and customer satisfaction. As a one-man operation, I personally handle 
						every project from initial consultation to final inspection, ensuring 
						consistent quality and attention to detail.
					</p>
					<p>
						Today, I'm proud to serve the Greater Toronto Area with hundreds of 
						satisfied customers and countless successful projects. Every job gets 
						my personal attention and commitment to excellence.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>Why Choose Me?</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>15+ years of hands-on experience</li>
						<li>Fully licensed and insured</li>
						<li>Personal attention to every project</li>
						<li>Quality materials from trusted suppliers</li>
						<li>Competitive, transparent pricing</li>
						<li>Free estimates and consultations</li>
						<li>Warranty on all work</li>
						<li>Direct communication - no middleman</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section style="background-color: var(--light-bg);">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>My Values</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-3">
				<div class="card">
					<h3><span class="icon">&#xE930;</span> Quality First</h3>
					<p>I never compromise on the quality of my work or materials. Every project is completed to the highest standards with my personal guarantee.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3><span class="icon">&#xE8E4;</span> Integrity</h3>
					<p>Honest communication, fair pricing, and transparent processes are the foundation of how I do business. You deal directly with me from start to finish.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3><span class="icon">&#xE77B;</span> Personal Service</h3>
					<p>As a one-man operation, I treat every home with respect and every project with the attention it deserves. Your satisfaction is my reputation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<div class="container">
			<h2>My Expertise</h2>
			<p class="section-description">
				With over 15 years specializing in exterior renovations, I have the knowledge 
				and experience to handle projects of any size and complexity - personally.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-2">
				<div class="card">
					<h3><span class="icon">&#xE80F;</span> Residential Services</h3>
					<p>I specialize in single-family homes and multi-unit properties, providing comprehensive exterior renovation services tailored to your specific needs.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3><span class="icon">&#xE779;</span> Direct Communication</h3>
					<p>When you work with me, you get direct access to the person doing the work. No sales teams, no subcontractors - just honest, reliable service from a skilled professional.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section style="background-color: var(--light-bg);">
		<div class="container text-center">
			<h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
			<p class="section-description">
				Contact me today to discuss your exterior renovation project and receive a free, no-obligation quote.
			</p>
			<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/contact/`} class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding-left: 0;
	}
	ul li::before {
		content: "\E930";
		font-family: 'Segoe Fluent Icons', 'Segoe MDL2 Assets';
		color: var(--primary-color);
		font-weight: normal;
		margin-right: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}
	ul li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.icon {
		font-family: 'Segoe Fluent Icons', 'Segoe MDL2 Assets';
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--primary-color);
		margin-right: 0.5rem;
		vertical-align: middle;
		font-weight: normal;
	}
</style>
